1
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:57,960
Come here. Come here.

2
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:00,240
What are you doing?

3
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,360
You won't regret following me.

4
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,519
In a few days,

5
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:06,120
I, Moo-yeol,

6
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,080
I'll make you a conferred wife.

7
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:09,400
Who's with you?

8
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,840
You forced me.

9
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,400
So what?

10
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,280
If I force you, you're mine too.

11
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:18,160
From now on, you'll always be.

12
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:21,560
Move aside. I'm going to the bridal chamber to serve.

13
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:49,479
Aren't you going to buy the guests a drink?

14
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:50,840
They are my subordinates.

15
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,640
It doesn't matter if you're late.

16
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:56,440
It's more exciting

17
00:01:57,039 --> 00:02:00,720
It makes my heart itch.

18
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,120
A lesson makes you wise.

19
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:13,360
I still remember

20
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,120
what you did last time.

21
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,320
General.

22
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,400
Cross-cupped wine.

23
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,120
General.

24
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,440
General, Moo-yeol is here.

25
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:40,079
Your wife is waiting for you.

26
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,400
Come in.

27
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,760
Yes, sir! Yes, sir!

28
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:50,920
General.

29
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,600
Say it.

30
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,120
As you expected,

31
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:58,200
Nine-head is the eldest son of the Helian Clan.

32
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,200
He Lian Jin.

33
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,320
Did you catch him and He Lian Cheng?

34
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,920
Not yet.

35
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,000
Idiot!

36
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,040
Calm down, General.

37
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,360
I gave you five thousand elites.

38
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,280
You can't even catch those scumbags of the Helian Clan.

39
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:14,920
Half of the 5,000 elites surrendered to He Lian Jin.

40
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:17,800
Most of our garrisons in Colorless City turned against him.

41
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:18,880
So...

42
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,440
Bastard!

43
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,720
You bastard!

44
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,960
You ungrateful bastard!

45
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,520
Pass my order.

46
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:30,400
Attack Colorless City tomorrow.

47
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,280
Before entering the capital,

48
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:35,840
I will destroy Colorless City.

49
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:36,400
Yes.

50
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,400
There are 200,000 soldiers in the North.

51
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:47,320
He Lian Jin.

52
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:52,040
General. Madam.

53
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,520
Please drink the couple wine.

54
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,200
Let's drink together.

55
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,320
Let's be united and grow old together.

56
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,400
Hahaha.

57
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,760
Baili Jinghong.

58
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:17,959
You are despicable!

59
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,040
Accept your fate, Your Highness.

60
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:23,080
Even if your magic is extraordinary,

61
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,960
you can’t resist

62
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:26,440
you can’t resist it.

63
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,240
Get out of here! Get out of here!

64
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,159
Get lost!

65
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:48,280
Your Highness, are you okay?

66
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,160
Momo.

67
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,680
You want to die?

68
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,400
Momo.

69
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,720
Your Highness, go!

70
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,760
Let go of me.

71
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,880
You'll die if you don't let go.

72
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,960
Your Highness, go!

73
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,960
Why?

74
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,840
Don't you hate me?

75
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,840
Ever since I met you,

76
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:36,320
I only see your kindness

77
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,040
and protection.

78
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,080
How can I hate you?

79
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,960
You are not a demon queen.

80
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,400
You are not.

81
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,960
Your Highness. Your Highness.

82
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,400
Your Highness.

83
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,040
Momo.

84
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,800
Nine-head.

85
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,640
No.

86
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,640
I should call you He Lian Jin.

87
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,800
Only I can detoxify your poison.

88
00:07:58,440 --> 00:08:00,720
You can't live even if I die.

89
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,640
Why did you marry him?

90
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:09,680
He can't force you because you have the Camp.

91
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,200
You're poisoned.

92
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:29,000
Because I don't want to wait anymore.

93
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,200
I've been in the palace for five years.

94
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,039
When I got the death certificate,

95
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,880
Shen Lian asked me to endure it.

96
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,440
I waited for her poison.

97
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:46,000
I surrendered to the throne.

98
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:49,240
I waited for Ji Hong Zhen's desire.

99
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,960
I want to wait for you this time.

100
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:56,200
but it’s Baili Jinghong’s wedding.

101
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,240
He Lian Jin.

102
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,160
You broke your promise.

103
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:12,440
Since then, I told myself

104
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,080
I won't wait for anyone.

105
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:19,400
I won't accept any other arrangement.

106
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,160
I want to seize power.

107
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,520
I want to go back to the capital.

108
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:26,720
I want to ascend the throne myself.

109
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,640
I want to be the Supreme Lord.

110
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,280
I want to be the best in the world.

111
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,000
The throne?

112
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:36,800
I'll get it for you.

113
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:08,560
Go find the general.

114
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:10,360
Someone rebelled at the wedding.

115
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:23,560
Ji Mingyue.

116
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:25,800
Do you know what you are doing?

117
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,040
I know very well.

118
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,520
Ji Mingyue.

119
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,560
Look carefully.

120
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,960
Do you know who I am?

121
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:10,760
The thief in the palace. It's really you.

122
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:12,560
Who else do you think it is?

123
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:01,600
I'll give you

124
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,160
whatever you want.

125
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,160
The military power is the same.

126
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:08,800
and the throne.

127
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,360
What's the condition?

128
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,120
I hope

129
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,200
after you ascend the throne,

130
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:18,680
you will be released

131
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:21,920
Release the Helian Clan.

132
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:24,880
Let them be free and never be slaves.

133
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,960
What if I say no?

134
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:36,880
I'm just kidding.

135
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:41,520
I promise you, He Lian Jin.

136
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:45,200
If I ascend the throne,

137
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,360
I will release the Helian family

138
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,840
and never be slaves.

139
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,280
The moon is the witness.

140
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:58,800
The moon is my witness.

141
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:16,440
I came back too late.

142
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:18,080
It’s not your fault.

143
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:23,360
Have you got all the trusted aides of Baili Jinghong?

144
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,280
Yes.

145
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,680
After all, he was my former colleague.

146
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:29,040
They'll disappear without blood.

147
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:31,760
I'm afraid they don't know what's good for them.

148
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:34,440
Let's go.

149
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,720
Let's go to the front hall.

150
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:37,840
You are in charge of the North Army.

151
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:38,960
Why are you still listening to the order?

152
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:41,440
We are not trying to rebel.

153
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,880
but to help the Empress Dowager.

154
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:46,280
to suppress the rebellion.

155
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:47,760
Got it?

156
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:01,160
Traitor! Traitor!

157
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:05,040
Traitor!

158
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,520
Traitor!

159
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,800
Lord Huo.

160
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:18,520
Decree.

161
00:16:16,560 --> 00:16:16,680
Jiaga.
